And she told me that she's
having a very happy time there

00:09:03.930 --> 00:09:04.920 align:middle line:90%
and no hauntings.

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:06.700 align:middle line:90%
So I'm happy to hear that.

00:09:06.700 --> 00:09:09.450 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: So they followed
the family, primarily,

00:09:09.450 --> 00:09:10.560 align:middle line:90%
I would think.

