negative didn't stay.

00:09:19.610 --> 00:09:22.510 align:middle line:84%
And I think that our
family just sort of--

00:09:22.510 --> 00:09:24.250 align:middle line:84%
my sisters, they
don't have anything

00:09:24.250 --> 00:09:25.480 align:middle line:90%
to do with the paranormal.

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:28.780 align:middle line:84%
They're totally happy, and
