and a less fearful way.

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:39.130 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And then at
what point, Courtney,

00:09:39.130 --> 00:09:42.460 align:middle line:84%
did you put together the
Haunted History Tours?

00:09:42.460 --> 00:09:47.980 align:middle line:84%
>>MCINVALE: I did that
