>>MCINVALE: (LAUGHING) No, no,
the real one in the Washington

00:10:04.070 --> 00:10:04.870 align:middle line:90%
Navy Yard.

00:10:04.870 --> 00:10:07.300 align:middle line:84%
I had gone to school
in Washington DC.

00:10:07.300 --> 00:10:10.210 align:middle line:84%
And I loved putting
together the pieces

00:10:10.210 --> 00:10:12.910 align:middle line:84%
and finding information
that no one else had ever

00:10:12.910 --> 00:10:14.900 align:middle line:90%
found about cases.

00:10:14.900 --> 00:10:18.230 align:middle line:84%
And so when I did
that, I thought,

00:10:18.230 --> 00:10:20.120 align:middle line:84%
this is what I want
to do for a job.

00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:21.250 align:middle line:90%
This is really fascinating.

00:10:21.250 --> 00:10:23.440 align:middle line:90%
And NCIS said, we're not hiring.

00:10:23.440 --> 00:10:26.080 align:middle line:84%
So the FBI was having
a hiring blitz,

00:10:26.080 --> 00:10:27.920 align:middle line:90%
and they saw my experience.

00:10:27.920 --> 00:10:28.720 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Perfect.

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:31.510 align:middle line:84%
>>MCINVALE: I
started with the FBI.

00:10:31.510 --> 00:10:36.280 align:middle line:84%
Unfortunately, for me,
because I was more focused

00:10:36.280 --> 00:10:38.800 align:middle line:84%
on the work I had
done at NCIS, I

00:10:38.800 --> 00:10:41.020 align:middle line:84%
got placed in
counterterrorism after I

00:10:41.020 --> 00:10:42.110 align:middle line:90%
finished the FBI Academy.

00:10:42.110 --> 00:10:42.910 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Really.

00:10:42.910 --> 00:10:44.350 align:middle line:84%
>>MCINVALE: Yes,
and I didn't feel

00:10:44.350 --> 00:10:46.840 align:middle line:84%
like I was particularly
knowledgeable

00:10:46.840 --> 00:10:50.870 align:middle line:84%
about counterterrorism, but that
was where they needed people.

00:10:50.870 --> 00:10:53.110 align:middle line:84%
And when I was
doing that, I just

00:10:53.110 --> 00:10:55.780 align:middle line:84%
didn't feel a
connection with my work.

00:10:55.780 --> 00:11:00.950 align:middle line:84%
And I more or less didn't like
going to an office from 9 to 5.

00:11:00.950 --> 00:11:01.750 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Who does.

00:11:01.750 --> 00:11:05.320 align:middle line:84%
>>MCINVALE: Right, it just
that was draining my soul.

00:11:05.320 --> 00:11:09.280 align:middle line:84%
So I thought maybe
I'll change my scenery.

00:11:09.280 --> 00:11:12.160 align:middle line:84%
And that's when I started
working for Homeland Security

00:11:12.160 --> 00:11:14.260 align:middle line:84%
because they had an
opportunity in Vermont,

00:11:14.260 --> 00:11:16.630 align:middle line:84%
and Vermont is lovely,
and my sister lived there.

00:11:16.630 --> 00:11:18.590 align:middle line:90%
And I could be closer to family.

00:11:18.590 --> 00:11:22.270 align:middle line:84%
And so I did that for a
while, but again, it was still

00:11:22.270 --> 00:11:24.220 align:middle line:90%
that 9 to 5 office job.

00:11:24.220 --> 00:11:27.280 align:middle line:90%
I just had better surroundings.

00:11:27.280 --> 00:11:29.290 align:middle line:84%
However, when I was there
at Homeland Security,

00:11:29.290 --> 00:11:30.370 align:middle line:90%
I met a woman.

00:11:30.370 --> 00:11:33.550 align:middle line:84%
I went on a ghost tour, and
she was running the ghost tour.

00:11:33.550 --> 00:11:34.840 align:middle line:90%
Her name is Thea Lewis.

00:11:34.840 --> 00:11:40.090 align:middle line:84%
And she was spreading
history, mysterious stories,

00:11:40.090 --> 00:11:41.380 align:middle line:90%
talking about these things.

00:11:41.380 --> 00:11:43.040 align:middle line:90%
She had books about it.

00:11:43.040 --> 00:11:44.920 align:middle line:84%
And when I was little,
I always thought

00:11:44.920 --> 00:11:46.240 align:middle line:90%
I wanted to be an author.

00:11:46.240 --> 00:11:48.600 align:middle line:84%
My parents read to me every
night when I was growing up,

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:49.400 align:middle line:90%
I wanted to write.

00:11:49.400 --> 00:11:50.110 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: You did it.

00:11:50.110 --> 00:11:50.910 align:middle line:90%
You did it.

00:11:50.910 --> 00:11:53.500 align:middle line:84%
>>MCINVALE: Yes,
and she inspired me.

00:11:53.500 --> 00:11:56.830 align:middle line:84%
I thought, she's interested
in history and mystery.

00:11:56.830 --> 00:11:59.770 align:middle line:84%
My father read me history
books when I would go to bed.

00:11:59.770 --> 00:12:02.260 align:middle line:90%
So I thought, this is the dream.

00:12:02.260 --> 00:12:04.120 align:middle line:84%
And I said, will you
have lunch with me

00:12:04.120 --> 00:12:05.860 align:middle line:90%
and tell me how you got started?

00:12:05.860 --> 00:12:07.240 align:middle line:90%
And she did.

00:12:07.240 --> 00:12:10.480 align:middle line:84%
And she said, you can
do this too Courtney.

00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:12.770 align:middle line:84%
And I said I'd love
to do this at home.

00:12:12.770 --> 00:12:14.920 align:middle line:84%
And so I went back
home to Connecticut,

00:12:14.920 --> 00:12:18.940 align:middle line:84%
and I started Seaside
Shadows Haunted History Tours

00:12:18.940 --> 00:12:23.020 align:middle line:84%
and started writing my
books and left the jobs

00:12:23.020 --> 00:12:25.150 align:middle line:90%
with the man behind.

00:12:25.150 --> 00:12:27.608 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And you still started
investigating ghosts at this

00:12:27.608 --> 00:12:28.408 align:middle line:90%
point--

00:12:28.408 --> 00:12:29.310 align:middle line:90%
>>MCINVALE: I did.

00:12:29.310 --> 00:12:30.110 align:middle line:90%
I did.

00:12:30.110 --> 00:12:31.443 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: --which is interesting.

00:12:31.443 --> 00:12:33.670 align:middle line:84%
We have a clip of you
using your special tools

00:12:33.670 --> 00:12:34.685 align:middle line:90%
to talk to ghosts.

00:12:34.685 --> 00:12:35.560 align:middle line:90%
>>MCINVALE: Yes, yes.

00:12:35.560 --> 00:12:36.250 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Let's watch this.

