00:13:00.880 --> 00:13:04.750 align:middle line:84%
And then also, in lieu of a
spirit box because there's

00:13:04.750 --> 00:13:07.510 align:middle line:84%
no signal here to help
generate the white noise,

00:13:07.510 --> 00:13:10.870 align:middle line:84%
we're going to be using
the Echo Vox, which

00:13:10.870 --> 00:13:15.350 align:middle line:84%
