- Where do we stand?

00:14:20.835 --> 00:14:24.300 align:middle line:90%


00:14:24.300 --> 00:14:26.450 align:middle line:90%
- [MUFFLED SPEECH]

00:14:26.450 --> 00:14:28.670 align:middle line:90%
- Four.

00:14:28.670 --> 00:14:32.660 align:middle line:90%
