00:14:32.660 --> 00:14:38.730 align:middle line:90%
- [MUFFLED SPEECH]

00:14:38.730 --> 00:14:42.100 align:middle line:90%
- When did you live here?

00:14:42.100 --> 00:14:45.400 align:middle line:90%
- [MUFFLED SPEECH]

00:14:45.400 --> 00:14:47.170 align:middle line:84%
- Did you hear that
male voice responding?

00:14:47.170 --> 00:14:48.100 align:middle line:90%
He said help.

00:14:48.100 --> 00:14:49.600 align:middle line:90%
What do you need help with?

00:14:49.600 --> 00:14:52.650 align:middle line:90%


00:14:52.650 --> 00:14:56.270 align:middle line:90%
- [MUFFLED SPEECH]

00:14:56.270 --> 00:14:58.292 align:middle line:90%
- Are you trapped here?

00:14:58.292 --> 00:15:00.260 align:middle line:90%
- [MUFFLED SPEECH]

00:15:00.260 --> 00:15:02.690 align:middle line:84%
- Yes, and I heard
Adam, as well.

00:15:02.690 --> 00:15:05.392 align:middle line:90%
Were you murdered here?

00:15:05.392 --> 00:15:09.160 align:middle line:90%
- [MUFFLED SPEECH]

00:15:09.160 --> 00:15:09.960 align:middle line:90%
- Did you hear yes?

00:15:09.960 --> 00:15:11.290 align:middle line:90%
